item.title: Prosecutors will retry man in death of Etan Patz, whose 1979 disappearance spotlighted missing kids
item.description: A notorious 1979 missing-child case will go to trial for a third time in New York City. Manhattan prosecutors vowed in a court filing Tuesday to retry the man whose murder conviction was recently overturned in the disappearance of 6-year-old Etan Patz.
